1
00:03:34,299 --> 00:03:36,210
Echo three to echo seven.

2
00:03:36,301 --> 00:03:38,212
Han, old buddy, do you read me?

3
00:03:38,303 --> 00:03:40,214
Han: Loud and clear, kid. What's up?

4
00:03:40,346 --> 00:03:41,346
I finished my circle.

5
00:03:41,431 --> 00:03:43,137
I don't pick up any life readings.

6
00:03:43,224 --> 00:03:46,216
There isn't enough life on this ice cube
to fill a space cruiser.

7
00:03:46,311 --> 00:03:48,142
Sensors are placed. I'm going back.

8
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,095
Right. I'll see you shortly.

9
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:52,126
There's a meteorite
that hit the ground near here.

10
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:54,311
I want to check it out.
It won't take long.

11
00:03:55,904 --> 00:03:59,146
Steady, girl. What's the matter?

12
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:00,525
You smell something?

13
00:04:41,533 --> 00:04:42,693
Han: Chewiel

14
00:04:42,784 --> 00:04:44,866
Chewie?

15
00:04:45,703 --> 00:04:46,943
Chewiel

16
00:04:50,291 --> 00:04:51,906
all right! Don't lose your temper.

17
00:04:52,001 --> 00:04:53,616
I'll come right back
and give you a hand.

18
00:05:14,941 --> 00:05:15,941
Solo?

19
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:17,606
No sign of life out there, general.

20
00:05:17,694 --> 00:05:18,979
The sensors are in place.

21
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,256
You'll know if anything comes around.

22
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,799
Rieekan: Commander Skywalker
reported in yet?

23
00:05:21,823 --> 00:05:24,155
No. He's checking out
a meteorite that hit near him.

24
00:05:24,701 --> 00:05:26,345
,

25
00:05:26,369 --> 00:05:28,430
It's going to be difficult to spot
approaching ships.

26
00:05:28,454 --> 00:05:30,661
General, I got to leave.
I can't stay anymore.

27
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,040
I'm sorry to hear that.

28
00:05:32,125 --> 00:05:33,269
Well, there's a price on my head.

29
00:05:33,293 --> 00:05:34,783
If I don't pay off jabba the hutt,

30
00:05:34,878 --> 00:05:36,084
I'm a dead man.

31
00:05:36,170 --> 00:05:38,252
A death Mark's
not an easy thing to live with.

32
00:05:39,465 --> 00:05:40,625
You're a good fighter, solo.

33
00:05:40,717 --> 00:05:41,877
I hate to lose you.

34
00:05:41,968 --> 00:05:43,253
Thank you, general.

35
00:05:51,728 --> 00:05:53,684
Well, your highness, guess this is it.

36
00:05:54,606 --> 00:05:55,891
That's right.

37
00:05:58,443 --> 00:06:01,025
Well, don't get all mushy on me.
So long, Princess.

38
00:06:03,656 --> 00:06:04,862
Han!

39
00:06:06,492 --> 00:06:08,403
Yes, your highnessness?

40
00:06:08,494 --> 00:06:09,984
