for immediate launch.

236
00:21:30,415 --> 00:21:31,415
Right, sir.

237
00:21:36,672 --> 00:21:37,707
Try it.

238
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:42,633
Oh! Turn it off! Turn it off!

239
00:21:42,719 --> 00:21:44,835
Turn it off!

240
00:21:45,389 --> 00:21:48,631
Droid: Sir, it will take quite a while
to evacuate the t-47s.

241
00:21:48,725 --> 00:21:49,786
Forget the heavy equipment.

242
00:21:49,810 --> 00:21:52,163
There's plenty of time to get
the smaller modules on the transports.

243
00:21:52,187 --> 00:21:53,187
Take care, sir.

244
00:21:53,272 --> 00:21:54,272
Thanks.

245
00:21:57,651 --> 00:22:00,518
Chewie, take care of yourself, okay?

246
00:22:04,533 --> 00:22:06,444
Okay, okay!

247
00:22:07,619 --> 00:22:09,155
Hi, kid.

248
00:22:09,329 --> 00:22:11,741
