251
00:22:15,878 --> 00:22:17,118
Yeah.

252
00:22:23,635 --> 00:22:24,841
Be careful.

253
00:22:25,596 --> 00:22:26,802
You, too.

254
00:22:33,687 --> 00:22:35,723
General, there's a fleet
of star destroyers

255
00:22:35,814 --> 00:22:37,475
coming out of hyperspace in sector four.

256
00:22:38,025 --> 00:22:40,607
Reroute all power to the energy shield.

257
00:22:40,944 --> 00:22:44,186
We gotta hold them
till all transports are away.

258
00:22:44,323 --> 00:22:45,688
Prepare for ground assault.

259
00:23:00,172 --> 00:23:02,003
Darth Vader: What is it, general?

260
00:23:02,090 --> 00:23:03,902
My lord, the fleet
has moved out of light speed.

261
00:23:03,926 --> 00:23:05,962
Comscan has detected
an energy field

262
00:23:06,053 --> 00:23:08,669
protecting an area of the sixth planet
of the hoth system.

263
00:23:08,764 --> 00:23:11,176
The field is strong enough
to deflect any bombardment.

264
00:23:11,266 --> 00:23:13,848
The rebels are alerted to our presence.

265
00:23:13,936 --> 00:23:17,099
Admiral ozzel came out of light speed
too close to the system.

266
00:23:17,189 --> 00:23:19,350
He... he felt surprise was wiser.

267
00:23:19,441 --> 00:23:21,773
He is as clumsy as he is stupid.

268
00:23:21,860 --> 00:23:25,102
General, prepare your troops
for a surface attack.

269
00:23:25,197 --> 00:23:26,778
Yes, my lord.

270
00:23:33,997 --> 00:23:35,282
Lord vader

271
00:23:35,374 --> 00:23:37,934
the fleet has moved out of light speed,
and we're preparing to...

272
00:23:39,378 --> 00:23:42,962
You have failed me
for the last time, admiral.

273
00:23:43,382 --> 00:23:44,542
Captain piett.

274
00:23:44,716 --> 00:23:46,206
Yes, my lord?

275
00:23:46,301 --> 00:23:49,293
Make ready to land our troops
beyond their energy field

276
00:23:49,388 --> 00:23:52,380
and deploy the fleet
so that nothing gets off the system.

277
00:23:52,474 --> 00:23:55,637
You are in command now, admiral piett.

278
00:23:55,727 --> 00:23:57,058
Thank you, lord vader.

279
00:23:58,814 --> 00:24:02,056
Leia: All troop carriers will assemble
at the north entrance.

280
00:24:02,150 --> 00:24:04,983
The heavy transport ships
will leave as soon as they're loaded.

281
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:07,152
Only two fighter escorts per ship.

282
00:24:07,239 --> 00:24:10,026
The energy shield
can only be opened for a short time,

283
00:24:10,117 --> 00:24:12,654
so you'll have to stay very close
to your transports.

284
00:24:12,744 --> 00:24:15,076
Two fighters against a star destroyer?

285
00:24:15,163 --> 00:24:17,154
The ion Cannon
will fire several shots

286
00:24:17,249 --> 00:24:20,241
to make sure that any enemy ships
will be out of your flight path.

287
00:24:20,669 --> 00:24:22,751
When you've gotten past
the energy shield,

288
00:24:22,838 --> 00:24:24,920
proceed directly
to the rendezvous point.

289
00:24:25,007 --> 00:24:26,668
Understood? All: Yeah.

290
00:24:26,758 --> 00:24:28,089
Good luck.

291
00:24:28,176 --> 00:24:30,087
Okay. Everybody to your stations.

292
00:24:30,178 --> 00:24:31,258
Let's go.

293
00:24:48,572 --> 00:24:51,860
Their primary target will be
the power generators.

294
00:24:52,075 --> 00:24:53,315
Prepare to open shield.

295
00:24:59,499 --> 00:25:01,660
Sir, rebel ships
are coming into our sector.

296
00:25:01,752 --> 00:25:03,834
Good. Our first catch of the day.

297
00:25:05,672 --> 00:25:07,663
Stand by, ion control.

298
00:25:08,967 --> 00:25:09,967
Fire.

299
00:25:25,150 --> 00:25:28,187
Man on pa:
The first transport is away.

300
00:25:28,278 --> 00:25:31,862
The first transport is away.

301
00:25:37,245 --> 00:25:39,110
Feeling all right, sir?

302
00:25:39,498 --> 00:25:41,204
Just like new, dak. How about you?

303
00:25:41,416 --> 00:25:44,453
Right now I feel I could take on
the whole empire myself.

304
00:25:44,544 --> 00:25:46,705
I know what you mean.

305
00:26:05,065 --> 00:26:06,180
Echo station three-t-eight.

306
00:26:06,441 --> 00:26:08,056
We've spotted imperial walkers.

307
00:26:08,151 --> 00:26:10,563
Controller:
Imperial walkers on the north Ridge.

308
00:26:33,051 --> 00:26:35,337
Echo station five-seven.
We're on our way.

309
00:26:40,851 --> 00:26:42,842
All right, boys, keep tight now.

310
00:26:42,936 --> 00:26:45,052
Luke, I have no approach vector.
I'm not set.

311
00:26:45,147 --> 00:26:46,728
Steady, dak.

312
00:26:46,815 --> 00:26:48,680
Attack pattern delta. Go now.

313
00:26:52,195 --> 00:26:53,935
All right. I'm coming in.

314
00:26:58,660 --> 00:26:59,991
Hobbie, you still with me?

315
00:27:22,559 --> 00:27:24,550
That armor's too strong for blasters.

316
00:27:26,938 --> 00:27:29,099
Rogue group,
use your harpoons and tow cables.

317
00:27:29,191 --> 00:27:31,631
Go for the legs. It might be
our only chance of stopping them.

318
00:27:33,570 --> 00:27:35,026
All right. Stand by, dak.

319
00:27:35,113 --> 00:27:37,980
Oh, Luke,
we've got a malfunction in fire control.

320
00:27:38,074 --> 00:27:40,030
I'll have to cut in the auxiliary.

321
00:27:40,118 --> 00:27:42,825
Just hang on. Hang on, dak.

322
00:27:42,913 --> 00:27:45,029
Get ready to fire that tow cable.

323
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:48,250
Ah!

324
00:27:50,337 --> 00:27:51,337
Dak?

325
00:27:51,421 --> 00:27:52,421
Dak!

326
00:28:15,654 --> 00:28:18,361
Veers: Yes, lord vader,
I've reached the main power generators.

327
00:28:18,448 --> 00:28:20,029
The shield will be down in moments.

328
00:28:20,116 --> 00:28:21,526
You may start your landing.

329
00:28:26,706 --> 00:28:27,866
Rogue three.

330
00:28:27,958 --> 00:28:29,073
Copy, rogue leader.

331
00:28:29,167 --> 00:28:31,078
Wedge, I've lost my gunner.

332
00:28:31,169 --> 00:28:32,375
You'll have to make this shot

333
00:28:32,879 --> 00:28:34,244
I'll cover for you.

334
00:28:34,339 --> 00:28:36,625
Set your harpoon.
Follow me on the next pass.

335
00:28:38,009 --> 00:28:40,000
Coming around, rogue leader.

336
00:28:42,847 --> 00:28:45,133
Steady, rogue two.

337
00:28:45,225 --> 00:28:46,305
Activate harpoon.

338
00:28:49,271 --> 00:28:50,932
Good shot, janson.

339
00:28:56,903 --> 00:28:59,189
- One more pass.
- Janson: Coming around, once more.

340
00:29:04,828 --> 00:29:07,035
Cable out. Let her go!

341
00:29:07,122 --> 00:29:08,987
Detach cable.

342
00:29:09,082 --> 00:29:10,197
Janson: Cable detached.

343
00:29:18,216 --> 00:29:19,956
Come on.

344
00:29:26,850 --> 00:29:28,215
Hah! That got him!

345
00:29:28,476 --> 00:29:29,841
I see it, wedge. Good work.

346
00:29:30,353 --> 00:29:32,765
I don't think we can protect
two transports at a time.

347
00:29:32,856 --> 00:29:35,097
It's risky,
but we can't hold out much longer.

348
00:29:35,191 --> 00:29:37,432
We have no choice.

349
00:29:37,527 --> 00:29:38,527
Launch patrol.

350
00:29:38,611 --> 00:29:40,226
Evacuate remaining ground staff.

351
00:29:40,655 --> 00:29:42,145
Chewie: Gahhh!

352
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:44,777
No, no! No.

353
00:29:44,868 --> 00:29:46,779
This one goes there.

354
00:29:46,870 --> 00:29:48,986
That one goes there, right?

355
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:52,618
R2, you take good care
of master Luke now, understand?

356
00:29:54,127 --> 00:29:56,368
And do take good care of yourself.

357
00:30:00,383 --> 00:30:01,919
Oh, dear. Oh, dear.

358
00:30:25,617 --> 00:30:27,824
All troops will debark
for ground assault,

359
00:30:27,911 --> 00:30:30,072
prepare to target the main generator.

360
00:30:34,084 --> 00:30:35,144
Rogue two, are you all right?

361
00:30:35,168 --> 00:30:37,500
Yeah. I'm with you, rogue leader.

362
00:30:37,587 --> 00:30:39,543
Well, set harpoon. I'll cover for you.

363
00:30:41,341 --> 00:30:42,421
Coming around.

364
00:30:42,509 --> 00:30:45,342
Watch that cross fire, boys.

365
00:30:45,428 --> 00:30:47,293
Set for position three.

366
00:30:47,555 --> 00:30:48,840
Steady.

367
00:30:48,932 --> 00:30:50,138
Stay tight and low.

368
00:30:50,225 --> 00:30:51,340
This is it!

369
00:30:51,434 --> 00:30:52,844
Aah!

370
00:30:56,940 --> 00:30:58,430
Hobbie!

371
00:30:58,525 --> 00:31:00,140
I've been hit!

372
00:31:42,402 --> 00:31:43,562
You all right?

373
00:31:43,987 --> 00:31:45,568
Why are you still here?

374
00:31:45,655 --> 00:31:47,236
Heard the command center
had been hit.

375
00:31:47,323 --> 00:31:48,634
You've got your clearance to leave.

376
00:31:48,658 --> 00:31:50,523
Don't worry. I'll leave.

377
00:31:52,454 --> 00:31:54,140
C-3po: Your highness,
we must take this last transport.

378
00:31:54,164 --> 00:31:55,164
It's our only hope.

379
00:31:55,248 --> 00:31:58,536
Send all troops in sector 12 to the
south slope to protect the fighters.

380
00:31:58,626 --> 00:31:59,832
Ah!

381
00:32:00,253 --> 00:32:02,209
Man on pa:
Imperial troops have entered the base.

382
00:32:02,297 --> 00:32:03,649
Imperial troops have entered...

383
00:32:03,673 --> 00:32:05,288
Come on. That's it.

384
00:32:05,967 --> 00:32:07,923
Give the evacuation code signal.

385
00:32:10,388 --> 00:32:11,673
And get to your transports!

386
00:32:11,931 --> 00:32:13,671
Ohl wait for Mel

387
00:32:13,933 --> 00:32:17,346
officer: Begin retreat! Fall back!

388
00:33:16,287 --> 00:33:17,652
Distance to power generators?

389
00:33:17,747 --> 00:33:19,032
Pilot: 17.28.

390
00:33:28,466 --> 00:33:30,422
Veers: Target. Maximum firepower.

391
00:33:56,536 --> 00:33:59,403
Transport, this is solo.
Better take off. I can't get to you.

392
00:33:59,497 --> 00:34:01,362
I'll get her out on the falcon.
Come on.

393
00:34:02,625 --> 00:34:04,707
B-b-but where are you going?

394
00:34:04,794 --> 00:34:05,909
Come back!

395
00:34:23,730 --> 00:34:24,730
Wait!

396
00:34:24,814 --> 00:34:27,396
Wait for me! Wait! Stop!

397
00:34:28,109 --> 00:34:29,724
- How typical.
- Han: Come on.

398
00:34:33,448 --> 00:34:34,608
Han: Hurry up, goldenrod.

399
00:34:34,699 --> 00:34:36,360
You're gonna be a permanent resident.

400
00:34:36,451 --> 00:34:37,782
C-3p0o: Wait! Wait!

401
00:34:56,471 --> 00:34:57,471
How's this?

402
00:34:57,972 --> 00:34:59,587
Would it help if I got out and pushed?

403
00:34:59,682 --> 00:35:00,842
Captain solo! Captain solo!

404
00:35:00,933 --> 00:35:01,933
It might.

405
00:35:03,311 --> 00:35:05,848
Sir, might I suggest that you...

406
00:35:06,731 --> 00:35:07,766
It can wait.

407
00:35:11,861 --> 00:35:14,301
This bucket of bolts is never gonna
get us past that blockade.

408
00:35:14,364 --> 00:35:16,696
This baby's got a few surprises
left in her, sweetheart.

409
00:35:25,667 --> 00:35:27,248
Come on! Come onl!

410
00:35:27,335 --> 00:35:29,872
Switch over.
Let's hope we don't have a burnout.

411
00:35:32,632 --> 00:35:33,632
See?

412
00:35:33,716 --> 00:35:36,356
Someday you're gonna be wrong,
and I just hope I'm there to see it.

413
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:39,840
Punch it!

414
00:35:57,657 --> 00:35:59,067
Luke: R2!

415
00:35:59,158 --> 00:36:01,615
Get her ready for takeoff.

416
00:36:04,455 --> 00:36:07,197
Man: Good luck, Luke.
See you at the rendezvous.

417
00:36:10,128 --> 00:36:12,744
Don't worry, r2.
We're going. We're going.

418
00:36:25,268 --> 00:36:26,599
There's nothing wrong, r2.

419
00:36:27,186 --> 00:36:28,722
I'm just setting a new course.

420
00:36:31,941 --> 00:36:33,556
We're not gonna regroup with the others.

421
00:36:34,736 --> 00:36:36,442
We're going to the dagobah system.
Going y

422
00:36:38,448 --> 00:36:40,188
yes, r27?

423
00:36:42,744 --> 00:36:43,779
That's all right.

424
00:36:43,870 --> 00:36:45,906
I'd like to keep it
on manual control for a while.

425
00:37:02,805 --> 00:37:03,965
I saw 'em! I saw 'em!

426
00:37:04,223 --> 00:37:05,303
Saw what?

427
00:37:05,391 --> 00:37:07,552
Star destroyers,
two of 'em coming right at us.

428
00:37:07,643 --> 00:37:09,179
Sir! Sir! Might I suggest...

429
00:37:09,270 --> 00:37:10,680
Shut him up or shut him down!

430
00:37:12,315 --> 00:37:14,271
Check the deflector shield.

431
00:37:15,234 --> 00:37:16,269
Great.

432
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,146
Well, we can still outmaneuver them.

433
00:37:22,658 --> 00:37:24,569
Take evasive action!

434
00:37:36,297 --> 00:37:37,912
Prepare to make the jump
to light speed.

435
00:37:38,007 --> 00:37:39,007
C-3po: But, sir!

436
00:37:39,467 --> 00:37:41,082
Leia: They're getting closer.

437
00:37:41,677 --> 00:37:43,793
Oh, yeah? Watch this.

438
00:37:47,016 --> 00:37:48,347
Watch what?

439
00:37:50,353 --> 00:37:51,388
I think we're in trouble.

440
00:37:51,479 --> 00:37:53,265
If I may say so, sir, I noticed earlier

441
00:37:53,356 --> 00:37:55,017
the hyperdrive motivator
has been damaged.

442
00:37:55,274 --> 00:37:56,889
It's impossible to go to light speed.

443
00:37:56,984 --> 00:37:58,099
We're in trouble.

444
00:38:04,325 --> 00:38:06,281
Gahhh!

445
00:38:06,369 --> 00:38:08,405
Alluvial dampers.

446
00:38:09,539 --> 00:38:11,700
Ow! That's not it.

447
00:38:11,791 --> 00:38:13,247
Bring me the hydrospanner!

448
00:38:16,963 --> 00:38:19,045
I don't know how
we're gonna get out of this one.

449
00:38:21,551 --> 00:38:22,711
Ow!

450
00:38:22,802 --> 00:38:23,882
Chewiel

451
00:38:28,057 --> 00:38:29,701
that wasn't a laser blast.
Something hit us.

452
00:38:29,725 --> 00:38:31,340
Han, get up here!

453
00:38:32,854 --> 00:38:34,060
Han: Come on, chewiel

454
00:38:35,022 --> 00:38:36,307
asteroids.

455
00:38:36,691 --> 00:38:37,851
Oh, no.

456
00:38:39,777 --> 00:38:41,313
Chewie, set two-seven-one.

457
00:38:41,737 --> 00:38:42,737
What are you doing?

458
00:38:43,865 --> 00:38:46,481
You're not actually going
into an asteroid field?

459
00:38:46,576 --> 00:38:48,407
They'd be crazy to follow us,
wouldn't they?

460
00:38:51,831 --> 00:38:53,492
You don't have to do this to impress me.

461
00:38:53,583 --> 00:38:55,824
Sir, the possibility
of successfully navigating

462
00:38:55,918 --> 00:38:58,409
an asteroid field
is approximately 3,720 to 1.

463
00:38:58,504 --> 00:39:00,085
Never tell me the odds!

464
00:39:22,445 --> 00:39:24,777
Look out!

465
00:39:27,950 --> 00:39:30,095
You said you wanted
to be around when I made a mistake.

466
00:39:30,119 --> 00:39:32,952
This could be it, sweetheart.
=I take it back.

467
00:39:33,039 --> 00:39:36,031
We're going to get pulverized
if we stay out here much longer.

468
00:39:36,125 --> 00:39:38,582
- Ain't gonna argue with that.
- C-3p0: Pulverized?

469
00:39:38,669 --> 00:39:40,147
I'm going in closer
to one of the big ones.

470
00:39:40,171 --> 00:39:41,752
- Closer?
- C-3p0o: Closer?

471
00:39:41,839 --> 00:39:42,874
Gahhh!

472
00:40:09,075 --> 00:40:11,053
C-3pqo: Oh, this is suicide!
There's nowhere to go.

473
00:40:11,077 --> 00:40:13,068
There. That looks pretty good.

474
00:40:13,371 --> 00:40:14,827
Leia: What looks pretty good?

475
00:40:14,914 --> 00:40:16,996
Han: Yeah, that'll do nicely.

476
00:40:17,458 --> 00:40:19,824
C-3p0o: Excuse me, ma'am,
but where are we going?

477
00:40:30,596 --> 00:40:32,928
I hope you know what you're doing.

478
00:40:33,015 --> 00:40:34,346
Yeah. Me, too.

479
00:40:42,942 --> 00:40:45,433
Yep, that's it. Dagobah.

480
00:40:47,822 --> 00:40:49,983
No, I'm not gonna change my mind
about this.

481
00:40:50,783 --> 00:40:53,525
I'm not picking up
any cities or technology.

482
00:40:53,619 --> 00:40:56,076
Massive life form readings, though.

483
00:40:57,039 --> 00:40:58,779
There's something alive down there.

484
00:41:00,501 --> 00:41:03,083
Yes. I'm sure
it's perfectly safe for droids.

485
00:41:10,553 --> 00:41:11,838
I know! I know!

486
00:41:12,513 --> 00:41:14,549
All the scopes are dead.
I can't see a thing.

487
00:41:15,599 --> 00:41:16,805
Just hang on.

488
00:41:16,892 --> 00:41:18,757
I'm gonna start the landing cycle.

489
00:42:12,615 --> 00:42:15,152
No, r2, you stay put.
I'll have a look around.

490
00:42:21,791 --> 00:42:22,791
R2i

491
00:42:25,127 --> 00:42:26,242
where are you?

492
00:42:29,590 --> 00:42:31,000
R2i

493
00:42:38,140 --> 00:42:39,755
You be more careful.

494
00:42:42,728 --> 00:42:45,561
R2, that way.

495
00:43:13,425 --> 00:43:14,710
R2i

496
00:43:42,288 --> 00:43:43,528
Oh, no.

497
00:43:44,874 --> 00:43:45,954
Are you all right?

498
00:43:46,041 --> 00:43:48,373
Come on.

499
00:43:50,629 --> 00:43:52,961
You were lucky to get out of there.

500
00:43:53,883 --> 00:43:54,998
Anything broken?

501
00:43:58,762 --> 00:44:01,299
If you're saying coming here
was a bad idea,

502
00:44:01,390 --> 00:44:02,926
I'm beginning to agree with you.

503
00:44:04,101 --> 00:44:06,183
R2, what are we doing here?

504
00:44:06,770 --> 00:44:11,480
It's like...
Something out of a dream or...

505
00:44:12,234 --> 00:44:13,849
I don't know.

506
00:44:14,236 --> 00:44:16,272
Maybe I'm just going crazy.

507
00:44:48,896 --> 00:44:49,976
Yes, admiral?

508
00:44:50,522 --> 00:44:52,763
Our ships have sighted
the millennium falcon, lord,

509
00:44:52,858 --> 00:44:55,520
but it has entered an asteroid field,
and we cannot risk...

510
00:44:55,611 --> 00:44:58,068
Asteroids do not concern me, admiral.

511
00:44:58,489 --> 00:45:01,356
I want that ship, not excuses.

512
00:45:01,742 --> 00:45:02,982
Yes, lord.

513
00:45:08,415 --> 00:45:11,452
I'm gonna shut down everything
but the emergency power systems.

514
00:45:11,543 --> 00:45:13,374
Sir, I'm almost afraid to ask,

515
00:45:13,462 --> 00:45:15,544
but does that include
shutting me down, too?

516
00:45:15,631 --> 00:45:17,872
No. I need you to talk to the falcon.

517
00:45:17,967 --> 00:45:19,798
Find out what's wrong
with the hyperdrive.

518
00:45:27,977 --> 00:45:31,265
Sir, it's quite possible
this asteroid is not entirely stable.

519
00:45:31,647 --> 00:45:33,433
Not entirely stable?

520
00:45:33,524 --> 00:45:35,480
I'm glad you're here
to tell us these things.

521
00:45:35,734 --> 00:45:39,067
Chewie, take the professor in the back
and plug him into the hyperdrive.

522
00:45:39,488 --> 00:45:42,070
Sometimes I just don't understand
human behavior.

523
00:45:42,157 --> 00:45:44,489
After all, I'm only trying to do my job.

524
00:45:49,331 --> 00:45:50,821
- Let go.
- Shh!

525
00:45:52,501 --> 00:45:53,911
Let go, please.

526
00:45:54,003 --> 00:45:55,243
Don't get excited.

527
00:45:55,337 --> 00:45:58,454
Captain, being held by you
isn't quite enough to get me excited.

528
00:45:59,216 --> 00:46:00,752
Sorry, sweetheart.

529
00:46:00,843 --> 00:46:02,799
I haven't got time for anything else.

530
00:46:37,838 --> 00:46:38,838
What?

531
00:46:38,922 --> 00:46:40,753
Ready for some power?

532
00:46:40,841 --> 00:46:41,876
Okay.

533
00:46:45,095 --> 00:46:46,426
I et's see now.

534
00:46:46,513 --> 00:46:48,299
Put that in there.

535
00:46:48,724 --> 00:46:49,884
There you go.

536
00:46:52,603 --> 00:46:54,468
Now all I gotta do is find this Yoda...

537
00:46:55,272 --> 00:46:56,853
If he even exists.

538
00:47:03,113 --> 00:47:06,196
It's really a strange place
to find a jedi master.

539
00:47:07,743 --> 00:47:09,608
This place gives me the creeps.

540
00:47:13,248 --> 00:47:14,533
Still...

541
00:47:16,377 --> 00:47:18,242
There's something familiar
about this place.

542
00:47:20,422 --> 00:47:21,958
I don't know.

543
00:47:22,049 --> 00:47:23,129
I feel like...

544
00:47:23,217 --> 00:47:24,627
Feel like what?

545
00:47:25,469 --> 00:47:27,175
Like we're being watched!

546
00:47:27,262 --> 00:47:30,174
Away put your weapon!
I mean you no harm,

547
00:47:31,266 --> 00:47:34,224
I am wondering... why are you here?

548
00:47:35,396 --> 00:47:37,307
I'm looking for someone.

549
00:47:37,398 --> 00:47:38,854
Looking?

550
00:47:38,941 --> 00:47:42,308
Found someone you have,
I would say, hmm?

551
00:47:42,611 --> 00:47:44,397
Right.

552
00:47:45,114 --> 00:47:47,856
Help you I can. Yes, mmm.

553
00:47:48,534 --> 00:47:49,944
I don't think so.

554
00:47:50,744 --> 00:47:52,450
I'm looking for a great warrior.

555
00:47:52,538 --> 00:47:53,744
Ah!

556
00:47:54,289 --> 00:47:56,120
A great warrior.

557
00:47:58,627 --> 00:48:00,538
Wars not make one great.

558
00:48:09,638 --> 00:48:10,878
Put that down.

559
00:48:10,973 --> 00:48:13,464
Hey! That's my dinner!

560
00:48:16,145 --> 00:48:19,387
How you get so big
eating food of this kind?

561
00:48:19,481 --> 00:48:21,601
Listen, friend, we didn't mean
to land in that puddle.

562
00:48:21,650 --> 00:48:23,390
And if we could get our ship out,
we would.

563
00:48:23,485 --> 00:48:24,587
But we can't, so why don't you...

564
00:48:24,611 --> 00:48:26,522
Cannot get your ship out. Hee hee hee!

565
00:48:26,613 --> 00:48:28,069
Hey, get out of there!

566
00:48:28,157 --> 00:48:29,397
Ah!

567
00:48:29,491 --> 00:48:31,527
No! Ooh!

568
00:48:31,618 --> 00:48:33,324
Hey, you could have broken this.

569
00:48:35,205 --> 00:48:36,205
Don't do that.

570
00:48:38,000 --> 00:48:39,410
Ohl

571
00:48:46,508 --> 00:48:48,499
You're making a mess.

572
00:48:50,512 --> 00:48:52,377
Hey, give me that!

573
00:48:52,473 --> 00:48:55,089
Mine, or I will help you not.

574
00:48:55,184 --> 00:48:57,015
I don't want your help.
I want my lamp back.

575
00:48:57,102 --> 00:48:59,102
I'm gonna need it
to get out of this slimy mudhole.

576
00:48:59,188 --> 00:49:01,019
Mudhole? Slimy?

577
00:49:01,106 --> 00:49:02,437
My home this is.

578
00:49:02,858 --> 00:49:05,395
Wha...

579
00:49:06,028 --> 00:49:07,564
Luke: R2, let him have it.

580
00:49:09,698 --> 00:49:11,984
Mine! Mine! Mine! Mine!

581
00:49:12,075 --> 00:49:13,155
Luke: R2!

582
00:49:16,497 --> 00:49:17,974
Now, will you move along, little fellow?

583
00:49:17,998 --> 00:49:19,454
We've got a lot of work to do.

584
00:49:19,541 --> 00:49:21,122
No! No, no!

585
00:49:21,210 --> 00:49:24,577
Stay and help you I will...
Find your friend.

586
00:49:25,172 --> 00:49:28,380
I'm not looking for a friend.
I'm looking for a jedi master.

587
00:49:28,759 --> 00:49:32,627
Oh. Jedi master. Yoda.

588
00:49:32,721 --> 00:49:34,336
You seek Yoda.

589
00:49:34,431 --> 00:49:35,546
You know him?

590
00:49:35,641 --> 00:49:39,133
Mmm. Take you to him I will.

591
00:49:39,228 --> 00:49:43,938
Yes, yes,
but now we must eat. Come.

592
00:49:44,650 --> 00:49:46,140
Good food. Come.

593
00:49:56,119 --> 00:49:57,984
Come, come.

594
00:49:59,790 --> 00:50:03,658
R2... stay and watch after the camp.

595
00:50:17,266 --> 00:50:20,008
Ohl where is r2 when I need him?

596
00:50:20,102 --> 00:50:23,139
Sir, I don't know where your ship
learned to communicate,

597
00:50:23,230 --> 00:50:25,016
but it has the most peculiar dialect.

598
00:50:25,107 --> 00:50:26,834
I believe, sir, it says
that the power coupling

599
00:50:26,858 --> 00:50:28,519
on the negative axis has been polarized.

600
00:50:28,610 --> 00:50:31,147
I'm afraid you'll have to replace it.

601
00:50:31,780 --> 00:50:34,442
Well, of course I'll have to replace it.

602
00:50:35,367 --> 00:50:37,153
Here! And, Chewie...

603
00:50:39,580 --> 00:50:41,780
I think we'd better replace
the negative power coupling.

604
00:51:04,146 --> 00:51:07,309
Hey, your worship,
I'm only trying to help.

605
00:51:07,399 --> 00:51:09,640
Would you please stop calling me that?

606
00:51:09,735 --> 00:51:11,817
Sure, Leia.

607
00:51:12,029 --> 00:51:14,020
You make it so difficult sometimes.

608
00:51:14,114 --> 00:51:16,070
I do. I really do.

609
00:51:16,241 --> 00:51:18,698
You could be a little nicer, though.

610
00:51:18,785 --> 00:51:21,697
Come on, admit it.
Sometimes you think I'm all right.

611
00:51:23,624 --> 00:51:26,115
Occasionally... maybe...

612
00:51:26,209 --> 00:51:28,666
When you aren't acting like a scoundrel.

613
00:51:28,754 --> 00:51:30,585
Scoundrel?

614
00:51:30,672 --> 00:51:32,287
Scoundrel?

615
00:51:34,426 --> 00:51:36,087
I like the sound of that.

616
00:51:37,095 --> 00:51:38,095
Stop that.

617
00:51:38,388 --> 00:51:39,753
Stop what?

618
00:51:39,848 --> 00:51:42,089
Stop that. My hands are dirty.

619
00:51:42,184 --> 00:51:44,550
My hands are dirty, too.
What are you afraid of?

620
00:51:44,645 --> 00:51:45,760
Afraid?

621
00:51:45,854 --> 00:51:47,560
You're trembling.

622
00:51:47,648 --> 00:51:49,354
I'm not trembling.

623
00:51:50,692 --> 00:51:53,024
You like me because I'm a scoundrel.

624
00:51:53,862 --> 00:51:56,103
There aren't enough scoundrels
in your life.

625
00:51:56,198 --> 00:51:57,938
I happen to like nice men.

626
00:51:58,617 --> 00:51:59,617
I'm a nice man.

627
00:51:59,826 --> 00:52:01,157
No, you're not. You're...

628
00:52:04,206 --> 00:52:07,869
Sir, sir! I've isolated
the reverse power flux coupling.

629
00:52:10,253 --> 00:52:11,459
Thank you.

630
00:52:11,546 --> 00:52:12,786
Thank you very much.

631
00:52:12,881 --> 00:52:14,712
Oh, you're perfectly welcome, sir.

632
00:52:20,764 --> 00:52:24,131
And that, lord vader, was the last time
they appeared in any of our scopes.

633
00:52:24,226 --> 00:52:25,703
Considering the amount of damage
we've sustained,

634
00:52:25,727 --> 00:52:27,137
they must have been destroyed.

635
00:52:27,229 --> 00:52:29,720
No, captain. They're alive.

636
00:52:30,315 --> 00:52:34,900
I want every ship available to sweep
the asteroid field until they are found.

637
00:52:38,824 --> 00:52:40,280
Lord vader.

638
00:52:41,076 --> 00:52:42,282
Yes, admiral. What is it?

639
00:52:42,869 --> 00:52:44,829
The emperor commands you
to make contact with him.

640
00:52:44,871 --> 00:52:47,362
Move the ship out of the asteroid field

641
00:52:47,457 --> 00:52:49,698
so that we can send
a clear transmission.

642
00:52:49,876 --> 00:52:51,286
Yes, my lord.

643
00:53:08,228 --> 00:53:10,685
What is thy bidding, my master?

644
00:53:11,732 --> 00:53:15,975
There is a great disturbance
in the force.

645
00:53:16,862 --> 00:53:18,398
I have felt it.

646
00:53:19,281 --> 00:53:21,738
We have a new enemy,

647
00:53:21,950 --> 00:53:25,943
the young rebel
who destroyed the death star.

648
00:53:26,663 --> 00:53:33,626
I have no doubt this boy
is the offspring of Anakin Skywalker.

649
00:53:33,837 --> 00:53:36,203
How is that possible?

650
00:53:36,298 --> 00:53:39,711
Search your feelings, lord vader.

651
00:53:39,801 --> 00:53:42,417
You will know it to be true.

652
00:53:43,221 --> 00:53:45,587
He could destroy us.

653
00:53:45,682 --> 00:53:47,798
He's just a boy.

654
00:53:47,893 --> 00:53:50,430
Obi-Wan can no longer help him.

655
00:53:50,729 --> 00:53:54,472
The force is strong with him.

656
00:53:55,317 --> 00:54:00,277
The son of Skywalker
must not become a jedi.

657
00:54:00,655 --> 00:54:02,691
If he could be turned,

658
00:54:02,783 --> 00:54:05,650
he would become a powerful ally.

659
00:54:06,578 --> 00:54:08,660
Yes

660
00:54:09,289 --> 00:54:12,827
he would be a great asset.

661
00:54:13,668 --> 00:54:15,909
Can it be done?

662
00:54:16,004 --> 00:54:19,371
He will join us or die, master.

663
00:54:36,650 --> 00:54:37,890
Look, I'm sure it's delicious.

664
00:54:37,984 --> 00:54:40,350
I just don't understand
why we can't see Yoda now.

665
00:54:40,445 --> 00:54:41,445
Patience!

666
00:54:41,530 --> 00:54:44,112
For the jedi,
it is time to eat as well.

667
00:54:44,199 --> 00:54:45,609
Hmm?

668
00:54:47,494 --> 00:54:49,701
Eat eat.

669
00:54:50,580 --> 00:54:51,660
Hot!

670
00:54:59,506 --> 00:55:01,542
Good food! Mmm, good, hmm?

671
00:55:01,633 --> 00:55:04,670
How far away is Yoda?
Will it take us long to get there?

672
00:55:04,761 --> 00:55:06,547
Not far. Yoda not far.

673
00:55:07,055 --> 00:55:09,671
Patience. Soon you will be with him.

674
00:55:12,227 --> 00:55:13,683
Root leaf

675
00:55:13,770 --> 00:55:15,260
I cook.

676
00:55:16,690 --> 00:55:20,274
Why wish you become jedi? Hmm? Hmm?

677
00:55:20,360 --> 00:55:21,975
Mostly because of my father, I guess.

678
00:55:22,070 --> 00:55:24,152
Ah, father.

679
00:55:24,239 --> 00:55:25,820
Powerful jedi was he.

680
00:55:25,907 --> 00:55:28,944
Hee hee. Mmm, powerful jedi.

681
00:55:29,035 --> 00:55:30,115
Oh, come on.

682
00:55:30,203 --> 00:55:31,363
How could you know my father?

683
00:55:31,413 --> 00:55:32,994
You don't even know who I am.

684
00:55:33,081 --> 00:55:35,914
I don't even know what I'm doing here.
We're wasting our time!

685
00:55:37,961 --> 00:55:39,826
I cannot teach him.

686
00:55:40,505 --> 00:55:42,461
The boy has no Patience.

687
00:55:42,716 --> 00:55:45,002
Obi-Wan: He will learn Patience.

688
00:55:49,848 --> 00:55:52,430
Much anger in him,

689
00:55:52,767 --> 00:55:54,473
like his father:

690
00:55:54,561 --> 00:55:57,303
Was I any different when you taught me?

691
00:55:59,524 --> 00:56:01,389
No.

692
00:56:01,568 --> 00:56:03,229
He is not ready.

693
00:56:03,320 --> 00:56:04,605
Yoda.

694
00:56:07,908 --> 00:56:09,364
I am ready.

695
00:56:09,492 --> 00:56:10,698
Ben... I can be a jedi.

696
00:56:10,785 --> 00:56:12,741
Ben, tell him I'm...

697
00:56:12,829 --> 00:56:14,365
Ready, are you?

698
00:56:14,456 --> 00:56:16,617
What know you ready?

699
00:56:16,708 --> 00:56:20,667
For 800 years have I trained jedi.

700
00:56:20,754 --> 00:56:24,417
My own counsel will I keep
on who is to be trained.

701
00:56:26,509 --> 00:56:30,468
A jedi must have
the deepest commitment, hmm?

702
00:56:30,555 --> 00:56:32,466
The most serious mind.

703
00:56:34,059 --> 00:56:37,176
This one a long time have I watched.

704
00:56:38,271 --> 00:56:41,263
All his life has he looked away...

705
00:56:41,483 --> 00:56:44,566
To the future, to the horizon.

706
00:56:44,653 --> 00:56:48,066
Never his mind on where he was,

707
00:56:48,156 --> 00:56:49,396
hmm?

708
00:56:49,491 --> 00:56:51,447
What he was doing.

709
00:56:51,534 --> 00:56:52,990
Hmph!

710
00:56:53,286 --> 00:56:54,366
Adventure.

711
00:56:54,454 --> 00:56:55,454
Hal

712
00:56:55,538 --> 00:56:56,869
excitement. Hal

713
00:56:57,207 --> 00:56:59,664
a jedi craves not these things.

714
00:57:00,543 --> 00:57:02,454
You are reckless!

715
00:57:02,545 --> 00:57:05,537
Obi-Wan: So was I, if you remember.

716
00:57:05,882 --> 00:57:07,292
He is too old.

717
00:57:08,760 --> 00:57:11,342
Yes, too old to begin the training.

718
00:57:12,013 --> 00:57:13,719
But I've learned so much.

719
00:57:21,398 --> 00:57:23,104
Will he finish what he begins?

720
00:57:23,566 --> 00:57:25,306
I won't fail you.

721
00:57:26,528 --> 00:57:28,064
I'm not afraid.

722
00:57:32,534 --> 00:57:34,195
You will be.

723
00:57:35,829 --> 00:57:37,490
You will be.

724
00:58:18,663 --> 00:58:19,869
Aah!

725
00:58:19,956 --> 00:58:21,617
Sir, if I may venture an opinion...

726
00:58:21,708 --> 00:58:23,394
Han: I'm not really interested
in your opinion, 3po.

727
00:58:23,418 --> 00:58:24,658
There's something out there.

728
00:58:25,670 --> 00:58:26,670
Where?

729
00:58:26,755 --> 00:58:27,755
Outside in the cave.

730
00:58:29,340 --> 00:58:30,750
There it is. Listen. Listen!

731
00:58:30,842 --> 00:58:31,877
I'm going out there.

732
00:58:31,968 --> 00:58:32,968
Are you crazy?

733
00:58:33,053 --> 00:58:34,113
I just got this bucket back together.

734
00:58:34,137 --> 00:58:35,781
I'm not going to let something
tear it apart.

735
00:58:35,805 --> 00:58:37,591
Oh! Then I'm going with you.

736
00:58:38,600 --> 00:58:40,056
I think it might be better

737
00:58:40,143 --> 00:58:42,179
if I stay behind and guard the ship.

738
00:58:42,270 --> 00:58:43,270
Oh, no.

739
00:58:58,036 --> 00:59:00,573
Leia: This ground sure feels strange.

740
00:59:01,831 --> 00:59:03,742
It doesn't feel like rock.

741
00:59:08,588 --> 00:59:10,388
Han: There's an awful lot
of moisture in here.

742
00:59:10,840 --> 00:59:11,920
Leia: I don't know.

743
00:59:12,550 --> 00:59:15,041
I have a bad feeling about this.

744
00:59:15,428 --> 00:59:16,508
Han: Yeah.

745
00:59:17,972 --> 00:59:18,972
Watch out!

746
00:59:20,225 --> 00:59:21,465
It's all right.

747
00:59:21,559 --> 00:59:22,559
It's all right.

748
00:59:22,644 --> 00:59:25,511
Yeah, that's what I thought. Mynock.

749
00:59:25,605 --> 00:59:28,847
Chewie, check the rest of the ship and
make sure there are no more attached,

750
00:59:28,942 --> 00:59:30,898
chewing on the power cables.

751
00:59:30,985 --> 00:59:32,441
Leia: Mynocks.

752
00:59:32,570 --> 00:59:34,810
Go on inside. We'll clean them off
if there are any more.

753
00:59:39,327 --> 00:59:40,327
Han!

754
00:59:42,789 --> 00:59:45,496
Aagghh! Go away, go away, beastly thing

755
00:59:45,583 --> 00:59:46,663
shoo! Shoo!

756
00:59:53,508 --> 00:59:55,419
Wait a minute...

757
01:00:17,157 --> 01:00:18,397
Let's get out of here!

758
01:00:18,491 --> 01:00:20,698
The empire is still out there!
I don't think...

759
01:00:20,785 --> 01:00:22,446
No time to discuss this in committee!

760
01:00:23,288 --> 01:00:25,279
I'm not a committeel

761
01:00:31,254 --> 01:00:33,961
You can't make the jump
to light speed in this asteroid field.

762
01:00:34,048 --> 01:00:36,209
Sit down, sweetheart! We're taking off!

763
01:00:40,638 --> 01:00:41,638
Look!

764
01:00:41,723 --> 01:00:42,883
I see it. I see it.

765
01:00:42,974 --> 01:00:43,974
C-3p0: We're doomed!

766
01:00:44,058 --> 01:00:45,298
Leia: The cave is collapsing.

767
01:00:45,393 --> 01:00:47,384
This is no cave. What?

768
01:01:20,011 --> 01:01:21,011
Yoda: Run!

769
01:01:21,888 --> 01:01:26,097
Yes! A jedi's strength
flows from the force.

770
01:01:26,184 --> 01:01:27,970
But beware of the dark side.

771
01:01:28,061 --> 01:01:29,767
Anger, fear, aggression...

772
01:01:29,854 --> 01:01:32,937
The dark side of the force are they,

773
01:01:33,024 --> 01:01:35,936
easily they flow,
quick to join you in a fight.

774
01:01:36,027 --> 01:01:38,313
If once you start down the dark path,

775
01:01:38,404 --> 01:01:40,440
forever will it dominate your destiny.

776
01:01:40,531 --> 01:01:41,862
Consume you it will,

777
01:01:41,950 --> 01:01:44,032
as it did Obi-Wan's apprentice.

778
01:01:44,369 --> 01:01:45,859
Vader.

779
01:01:46,746 --> 01:01:48,156
Is the dark side stronger?

780
01:01:48,248 --> 01:01:49,738
No, no.

781
01:01:50,041 --> 01:01:51,121
No.

782
01:01:51,209 --> 01:01:53,746
Quicker, easier, more seductive.

783
01:01:54,629 --> 01:01:56,711
But how am I to know
the good side from the bad?

784
01:01:56,798 --> 01:02:00,290
You will know when you are calm,

785
01:02:00,385 --> 01:02:01,966
at peace,

786
01:02:02,262 --> 01:02:03,752
passive.

787
01:02:03,846 --> 01:02:08,886
Hmm. A jedi uses the force
for knowledge and defense,

788
01:02:09,352 --> 01:02:11,092
never for attack.

789
01:02:11,187 --> 01:02:12,227
But tell me why I can't...

790
01:02:12,272 --> 01:02:14,308
No, no. There is no why.

791
01:02:14,649 --> 01:02:17,186
Nothing more will I teach you today.

792
01:02:17,735 --> 01:02:19,896
Clear your mind of questions.

793
01:02:42,468 --> 01:02:44,584
There's something not right here.

794
01:02:48,599 --> 01:02:50,180
I feel cold...

795
01:02:50,476 --> 01:02:51,556
Death.

796
01:02:51,644 --> 01:02:53,726
That place...

797
01:02:53,813 --> 01:02:56,930
Is strong with the dark side
of the force.

798
01:02:57,275 --> 01:02:59,516
A domain of evil it is.

799
01:03:00,945 --> 01:03:02,685
In you must go.

800
01:03:03,489 --> 01:03:05,275
What's in there?

801
01:03:07,535 --> 01:03:09,400
Only what you take with you.

802
01:03:13,875 --> 01:03:15,115
Your weapons...

803
01:03:15,793 --> 01:03:17,658
You will not need them.

804
01:05:45,610 --> 01:05:46,610
Hmph.

805
01:05:57,330 --> 01:05:59,787
Bounty hunters.
We don't need their scum.

806
01:05:59,874 --> 01:06:01,080
Yes, sir.

807
01:06:01,167 --> 01:06:03,249
Those rebels won't escape us.

808
01:06:08,758 --> 01:06:11,716
Sir, we have a priority signal
from the star destroyer avenger.

809
01:06:11,802 --> 01:06:13,133
Right.

810
01:06:13,679 --> 01:06:15,965
Darth Vader:
There will be a substantial reward

811
01:06:16,057 --> 01:06:19,595
for the one who finds
the millennium falcon.

812
01:06:19,685 --> 01:06:22,677
You are free to use
any methods necessary,

813
01:06:22,897 --> 01:06:25,013
but I want them alive.

814
01:06:25,107 --> 01:06:27,439
No disintegrations.

815
01:06:27,527 --> 01:06:28,607
Boba: As you wish.

816
01:06:28,694 --> 01:06:30,059
Piett: Lord vader:

817
01:06:31,572 --> 01:06:33,608
My lord, we have them.

818
01:06:38,246 --> 01:06:41,363
C-3p0o: Oh, thank goodness
we're coming out of the asteroid field.

819
01:06:46,295 --> 01:06:48,411
Han: Let's get out of here.
Ready for light speed?

820
01:06:48,965 --> 01:06:50,125
One...

821
01:06:50,216 --> 01:06:51,956
Two...

822
01:06:52,051 --> 01:06:53,211
Threel

823
01:06:58,766 --> 01:07:00,176
It's not fair.

824
01:07:00,268 --> 01:07:01,599
Gahhh!

825
01:07:03,604 --> 01:07:06,095
Transfer circuits aren't working.
It's not my fault!

826
01:07:06,190 --> 01:07:07,190
No light speed?

827
01:07:07,275 --> 01:07:09,186
It's not my fault.

828
01:07:13,990 --> 01:07:16,051
C-3po: Sir, we've just lost
the main rear deflector shield.

829
01:07:16,075 --> 01:07:18,395
One more direct hit
on the back quarter and we're done for.

830
01:07:18,536 --> 01:07:19,616
Turn her around.

831
01:07:19,787 --> 01:07:21,072
I said, turn her around.

832
01:07:21,163 --> 01:07:22,683
I'm going to put all power
in the front shield.

833
01:07:22,707 --> 01:07:23,809
You're going to attack them?

834
01:07:23,833 --> 01:07:24,873
Sir, the odds of surviving

835
01:07:24,959 --> 01:07:26,853
a direct assault on
an imperial star destroyer...

836
01:07:26,877 --> 01:07:28,833
- Shut up!
- Gaahh!

837
01:07:35,511 --> 01:07:37,502
They're moving to attack position.

838
01:07:39,890 --> 01:07:41,050
Shields up.

839
01:07:47,148 --> 01:07:49,139
Track them.
They may come around for another pass.

840
01:07:49,233 --> 01:07:51,565
Captain needa, the ship
no longer appears on our scopes.

841
01:07:52,028 --> 01:07:53,564
They can't have disappeared.

842
01:07:54,071 --> 01:07:56,278
No ship that small
has a cloaking device.

843
01:07:56,365 --> 01:07:57,855
Well, there's no trace of them, sir.

844
01:07:57,950 --> 01:08:00,066
Captain, lord vader
demands an update on the pursuit.

845
01:08:02,663 --> 01:08:04,403
Get a shuttle ready.

846
01:08:05,207 --> 01:08:07,102
I shall assume full responsibility
for losing them

847
01:08:07,126 --> 01:08:08,741
and apologize to lord vader.

848
01:08:09,170 --> 01:08:10,751
Meanwhile, continue to scan the area.

849
01:08:11,172 --> 01:08:12,662
Yes, captain needa.

850
01:08:17,178 --> 01:08:19,419
Yoda: Use the force.

851
01:08:19,513 --> 01:08:20,513
Yes.

852
01:08:26,020 --> 01:08:27,601
Now, the stone...

853
01:08:32,026 --> 01:08:34,062
Feel it.

854
01:08:45,247 --> 01:08:47,112
Concentrate!

855
01:09:01,847 --> 01:09:05,135
Oh, no. We'll never get it out now.

856
01:09:05,226 --> 01:09:06,841
So certain are you.

857
01:09:10,815 --> 01:09:13,898
Always with you it cannot be done.

858
01:09:15,403 --> 01:09:17,394
Hear you nothing that I say?

859
01:09:17,488 --> 01:09:19,524
Master, moving stones around
is one thing.

860
01:09:19,615 --> 01:09:21,230
This is totally different.

861
01:09:21,617 --> 01:09:23,278
No! No different!

862
01:09:23,619 --> 01:09:25,655
Only different in your mind.

863
01:09:25,913 --> 01:09:29,497
You must unlearn what you have learned.

864
01:09:30,584 --> 01:09:32,165
All right. I'll give it a try.

865
01:09:32,253 --> 01:09:33,834
No! Try not.

866
01:09:34,338 --> 01:09:36,294
Do.

867
01:09:36,382 --> 01:09:37,622
Or do not.

868
01:09:38,008 --> 01:09:39,623
There is no try.

869
01:10:30,220 --> 01:10:30,770
I can't. I¢'s too big.

870
01:10:30,771 --> 01:10:34,262
Size matters not. Look at me.

871
01:10:34,356 --> 01:10:36,563
Judge me by my size, do you?

872
01:10:37,735 --> 01:10:39,271
Hmph!

873
01:10:39,361 --> 01:10:41,522
And well you should not,

874
01:10:41,989 --> 01:10:44,731
for my ally is the force.

875
01:10:44,825 --> 01:10:47,737
And a powerful ally it is.

876
01:10:48,037 --> 01:10:50,198
Life creates it,

877
01:10:50,664 --> 01:10:52,154
makes it grow.

878
01:10:53,584 --> 01:10:56,747
Its energy surrounds us...

879
01:10:57,296 --> 01:10:58,752
And binds us.

880
01:10:59,006 --> 01:11:01,167
Luminous beings are we,

881
01:11:01,258 --> 01:11:02,998
not this crude matter:

882
01:11:03,719 --> 01:11:07,337
You must feel the force around you.

883
01:11:07,598 --> 01:11:10,715
Here, between you, me,

884
01:11:11,268 --> 01:11:14,635
the tree, the rock, everywhere!

885
01:11:15,314 --> 01:11:16,599
Yes.

886
01:11:17,399 --> 01:11:21,108
Even between the land and the ship.

887
01:11:26,033 --> 01:11:28,024
You want the impossible.

888
01:13:15,809 --> 01:13:16,809
I don't...

889
01:13:16,894 --> 01:13:19,226
I don't believe it.

890
01:13:19,855 --> 01:13:22,471
That is why you fail.

891
01:13:41,794 --> 01:13:45,878
Apology accepted, captain needa.

892
01:13:53,639 --> 01:13:55,595
Lord vader, our ships have completed

893
01:13:55,683 --> 01:13:57,283
their scan of the area
and found nothing.

894
01:13:57,351 --> 01:13:59,342
If the millennium falcon
went into light speed

895
01:13:59,436 --> 01:14:01,164
it'll be on the other side
of the galaxy by now.

896
01:14:01,188 --> 01:14:02,348
Alert all commands.

897
01:14:02,856 --> 01:14:07,566
Calculate every possible destination
along their last known trajectory.

898
01:14:07,653 --> 01:14:08,893
Yes, my lord. We'll find them.

899
01:14:08,988 --> 01:14:11,024
Don't fail me again...

900
01:14:12,032 --> 01:14:13,112
Admiral.

901
01:14:15,786 --> 01:14:17,401
Alert all commands.

902
01:14:17,496 --> 01:14:19,157
Deploy the fleet.

903
01:14:33,887 --> 01:14:36,219
Captain solo,
this time you've gone too far.

904
01:14:36,306 --> 01:14:37,421
Gahhh!

905
01:14:37,516 --> 01:14:40,633
No, I will not be quiet, Chewbacca.
Why doesn't anyone listen to me?

906
01:14:40,728 --> 01:14:42,088
The fleet's beginning to break up.

907
01:14:42,896 --> 01:14:45,512
Go back and stand by
the manual release for the landing claw.

908
01:14:48,027 --> 01:14:50,188
C-3pq: I really don't see
how that's going to help.

909
01:14:50,404 --> 01:14:53,862
Surrender is a perfectly acceptable
alternative in extreme circumstances.

910
01:14:53,949 --> 01:14:55,814
The empire may be gracious enough...

911
01:14:55,909 --> 01:14:56,909
Thank you.

912
01:14:56,994 --> 01:14:58,763
What do you have in your mind
for your next move?

913
01:14:58,787 --> 01:15:00,698
If they follow standard
imperial procedure,

914
01:15:00,789 --> 01:15:02,809
they'll dump their garbage
before they go to light speed,

915
01:15:02,833 --> 01:15:04,744
and then we just float away.

916
01:15:04,835 --> 01:15:07,542
With the rest of the garbage.
Then what?

917
01:15:10,758 --> 01:15:11,758
Any ideas?

918
01:15:11,842 --> 01:15:13,173
Where are we?

919
01:15:13,260 --> 01:15:14,750
The anoat system.

920
01:15:14,845 --> 01:15:16,756
I know that system.
There's not much there.

921
01:15:16,847 --> 01:15:20,715
No. Well, wait. This is interesting.

922
01:15:20,809 --> 01:15:21,889
Lando.

923
01:15:21,977 --> 01:15:23,513
Lando system?

924
01:15:23,604 --> 01:15:26,846
Lando's not a system.
He's a man. Lando calrissian.

925
01:15:27,191 --> 01:15:30,274
He's a cardplayer, gambler, scoundrel.

926
01:15:30,360 --> 01:15:32,351
You'd like him. Thanks.

927
01:15:32,446 --> 01:15:35,609
Bespin. It's pretty far,
but I think we can make it.

928
01:15:36,241 --> 01:15:37,902
A mining colony?

929
01:15:37,993 --> 01:15:40,029
Yeah, a tibanna gas mine.

930
01:15:40,454 --> 01:15:43,036
Lando conned somebody out of it.

931
01:15:43,123 --> 01:15:45,956
We go back a long way,
lando and me.

932
01:15:46,794 --> 01:15:48,000
Can you trust him?

933
01:15:48,087 --> 01:15:52,421
No. But he's got no love for the empire,
I can tell you that.

934
01:15:52,508 --> 01:15:55,545
Here we go, Chewie. Stand by.

935
01:15:55,677 --> 01:15:56,757
Detach.

936
01:16:03,977 --> 01:16:05,467
Leia: You do have your moments.

937
01:16:05,896 --> 01:16:07,227
Not many of them,

938
01:16:07,314 --> 01:16:08,975
but you do have them.

939
01:16:43,600 --> 01:16:45,261
Yoda: Concentrate.

940
01:16:45,352 --> 01:16:48,640
Feel the force flow.

941
01:16:48,730 --> 01:16:50,891
Yes.

942
01:16:58,198 --> 01:16:59,278
Good.

943
01:17:00,117 --> 01:17:01,607
Calm.

944
01:17:01,702 --> 01:17:03,112
Yes.

945
01:17:03,704 --> 01:17:06,662
Through the force, things you will see.

946
01:17:06,748 --> 01:17:10,206
Other places. The future. The past.

947
01:17:10,294 --> 01:17:12,876
Old friends long gone.

948
01:17:15,048 --> 01:17:16,288
Han?

949
01:17:16,800 --> 01:17:17,880
Leia!

950
01:17:23,307 --> 01:17:24,797
Control, control.

951
01:17:24,892 --> 01:17:26,803
You must learn control!

952
01:17:29,771 --> 01:17:33,059
I saw... l saw a city in the clouds.

953
01:17:34,776 --> 01:17:37,267
Friends you have there.

954
01:17:38,238 --> 01:17:39,318
They were in pain.

955
01:17:40,157 --> 01:17:41,897
It is the future you see.

956
01:17:43,410 --> 01:17:44,410
Future?

957
01:17:53,045 --> 01:17:54,330
Will they die?

958
01:17:57,674 --> 01:17:59,164
Difficult to see.

959
01:18:00,052 --> 01:18:02,043
Always in motion is the future.

960
01:18:05,015 --> 01:18:06,721
I've got to go to them.

961
01:18:11,313 --> 01:18:13,804
If you leave now, help them you could,

962
01:18:15,359 --> 01:18:18,977
but you would destroy all
for which they have fought and suffered.

963
01:18:32,793 --> 01:18:35,876
No, I don't have a landing permit.

964
01:18:35,963 --> 01:18:39,876
I'm trying to reach lando calrissian.

965
01:18:39,967 --> 01:18:42,049
Wait a minute! Let me explain!

966
01:18:42,135 --> 01:18:43,947
Man: You will not deviate
from your present course.

967
01:18:43,971 --> 01:18:45,371
C-3p0o: Rather touchy, aren't they?

968
01:18:45,472 --> 01:18:47,008
I thought you knew this person.

969
01:18:47,099 --> 01:18:49,010
Gaah!

970
01:18:49,768 --> 01:18:50,928
That was a long time ago.

971
01:18:51,019 --> 01:18:52,429
I'm sure he's forgotten about that.

972
01:19:01,196 --> 01:19:04,939
Man: Permission granted to land
on platform 3-2-7.

973
01:19:05,033 --> 01:19:06,398
Thank you.

974
01:19:07,202 --> 01:19:08,408
Nothing to worry about.

975
01:19:08,495 --> 01:19:10,201
We go way back, lando and me.

976
01:19:10,706 --> 01:19:12,071
Who's worried?

977
01:20:00,505 --> 01:20:02,245
C-3p0o: Oh. No one to meet us.

978
01:20:03,550 --> 01:20:04,585
I don't like this.

979
01:20:05,886 --> 01:20:07,126
Han: Well, what would you like?

980
01:20:07,220 --> 01:20:08,926
C-3pqo: They did let us land.

981
01:20:09,014 --> 01:20:11,676
Look, don't worry.
Everything's going to be fine.

982
01:20:11,767 --> 01:20:12,927
Trust me.

983
01:20:17,856 --> 01:20:19,721
See? My friend.

984
01:20:24,529 --> 01:20:26,485
Keep your eyes open, huh?

985
01:20:26,907 --> 01:20:28,488
Gahhh!

986
01:20:29,034 --> 01:20:30,149
Han: Hey!

987
01:20:30,786 --> 01:20:31,992
Why, you slimy,

988
01:20:32,079 --> 01:20:34,786
double-crossing, no-good swindler.

989
01:20:35,415 --> 01:20:39,203
You've got a lot of guts coming here
after what you pulled.

990
01:20:50,263 --> 01:20:53,630
How you doin', you old pirate?
So good to see you!

991
01:20:55,018 --> 01:20:56,929
C-3p0o: Well, he seems very friendly.

992
01:20:57,020 --> 01:20:58,020
Yes.

993
01:20:58,105 --> 01:21:00,096
Very friendly.

994
01:21:00,190 --> 01:21:01,475
What are you doing here?

995
01:21:01,566 --> 01:21:04,023
Ah, repairs.
I thought you could help me out.

996
01:21:04,111 --> 01:21:05,296
What have you done to my ship?

997
01:21:05,320 --> 01:21:06,320
Your ship?

998
01:21:06,571 --> 01:21:08,186
Hey, remember,

999
01:21:08,281 --> 01:21:10,363
you lost her to me fair and square.

1000
01:21:10,867 --> 01:21:12,323
And how you doin', Chewbacca?

1001
01:21:12,411 --> 01:21:13,411
Gahh!

1002
01:21:13,495 --> 01:21:15,095
You still hanging around
with this loser?

1003
01:21:15,414 --> 01:21:16,904
Gahhh!

1004
01:21:18,250 --> 01:21:20,536
Hello. What have we here?

1005
01:21:21,378 --> 01:21:23,039
Welcome, I'm lando calrissian.

1006
01:21:23,130 --> 01:21:24,916
I'm the administrator of this facility.

1007
01:21:25,298 --> 01:21:26,913
And who might you be?

1008
01:21:27,008 --> 01:21:28,088
Leia.

1009
01:21:28,593 --> 01:21:30,049
Welcome, Leia.

1010
01:21:32,973 --> 01:21:36,261
All right, all right, you old smoothie.

1011
01:21:36,351 --> 01:21:39,468
Hello, sir. I am c-3po,
human-cyborg relations.

1012
01:21:39,563 --> 01:21:40,894
My facilities are at your...

1013
01:21:41,773 --> 01:21:42,888
Well, really!

1014
01:21:42,983 --> 01:21:44,644
Lando: What's wrong with the falcon?

1015
01:21:44,734 --> 01:21:45,734
Han: Hyperdrive.

1016
01:21:45,819 --> 01:21:47,539
- I'll get my people to work on her.
- Good.

1017
01:21:47,571 --> 01:21:49,311
That ship saved my life
quite a few times.

1018
01:21:49,406 --> 01:21:52,318
She's the fastest
hunk of junk in the galaxy.

1019
01:21:53,285 --> 01:21:56,118
Han: How's the gas mine?
Still paying off for you?

1020
01:21:56,204 --> 01:21:57,515
Lando: Oh, not as well as I'd like.

1021
01:21:57,539 --> 01:21:59,905
We're a small outpost
and not very self-sufficient.

1022
01:22:00,000 --> 01:22:04,460
I've had supply problems of every kind.
I've had labor difficulties.

1023
01:22:04,546 --> 01:22:06,207
What's so funny?

1024
01:22:06,840 --> 01:22:08,171
You. Listen to you.

1025
01:22:08,675 --> 01:22:10,040
You sound like a businessman,

1026
01:22:10,135 --> 01:22:11,420
a responsible leader.

1027
01:22:11,678 --> 01:22:13,839
Who'd have thought that, huh?

1028
01:22:13,930 --> 01:22:16,387
Seeing you brings back a few things.

1029
01:22:16,892 --> 01:22:17,927
Yeah.

1030
01:22:18,185 --> 01:22:19,925
Yeah, I'm responsible these days.

1031
01:22:21,104 --> 01:22:23,595
It's the price you pay
for being successful.

1032
01:22:26,234 --> 01:22:28,316
C-3p0: Ooh. Nice to see a familiar face.

1033
01:22:28,403 --> 01:22:29,403
E chu ta!

1034
01:22:29,488 --> 01:22:30,773
How rude!

1035
01:22:32,574 --> 01:22:34,656
That sounds like an rz unit in there.

1036
01:22:34,743 --> 01:22:36,153
I wonder if .. Hello?

1037
01:22:38,497 --> 01:22:39,828
How interesting.

1038
01:22:39,915 --> 01:22:41,075
Man: Who are you?

1039
01:22:41,166 --> 01:22:43,407
Oh, my! I... I'm terribly sorry.

1040
01:22:43,502 --> 01:22:44,708
I didn't mean to intrude.

1041
01:22:44,794 --> 01:22:45,909
No, please don't get up.

1042
01:22:52,219 --> 01:22:53,550
Gahhh.

1043
01:23:04,105 --> 01:23:06,596
Luke, you must complete the training.

1044
01:23:07,025 --> 01:23:10,483
I can't keep the vision out of my head.
They're my friends. I got to help them.

1045
01:23:10,570 --> 01:23:12,731
You must not go.

1046
01:23:12,822 --> 01:23:14,653
But han and Leia will die if I don't.

1047
01:23:14,741 --> 01:23:16,151
Obi-Wan: You don't know that

1048
01:23:18,620 --> 01:23:20,531
even Yoda cannot see their fate.

1049
01:23:21,623 --> 01:23:22,988
But I can help them.

1050
01:23:23,083 --> 01:23:24,414
I feel the force.

1051
01:23:24,501 --> 01:23:26,082
But you cannot control it.

1052
01:23:26,461 --> 01:23:28,577
This is a dangerous time for you,

1053
01:23:29,005 --> 01:23:32,497
when you will be tempted
by the dark side of the force.

1054
01:23:32,592 --> 01:23:35,550
Yes! Yes! To Obi-Wan you listen.

1055
01:23:36,346 --> 01:23:40,134
The cave.
Remember your failure at the cave.

1056
01:23:40,225 --> 01:23:42,386
But I've learned so much since then.

1057
01:23:42,477 --> 01:23:44,957
Master Yoda, I promise to return
and to finish what I've begun.

1058
01:23:45,021 --> 01:23:46,261
You have my word.

1059
01:23:47,399 --> 01:23:50,186
It is you and your abilities
the emperor wants.

1060
01:23:50,277 --> 01:23:53,110
That is why your friends
are made to suffer.

1061
01:23:54,239 --> 01:23:56,195
That's why I have to go.

1062
01:23:56,533 --> 01:24:01,573
Luke, I don't want to lose you
to the emperor the way I lost vader.

1063
01:24:01,955 --> 01:24:03,286
You won't.

1064
01:24:03,832 --> 01:24:05,288
Stopped they must be.

1065
01:24:05,375 --> 01:24:07,661
On this all depends.

1066
01:24:08,044 --> 01:24:10,205
Only a fully trained jedi knight,

1067
01:24:10,297 --> 01:24:12,128
with the force as his ally,

1068
01:24:12,215 --> 01:24:14,706
will conquer vader and his emperor.

1069
01:24:15,010 --> 01:24:17,046
If you end your training now,

1070
01:24:17,345 --> 01:24:21,384
if you choose the quick
and easy path, as vader did,

1071
01:24:21,641 --> 01:24:24,223
you will become an agent of evil.

1072
01:24:24,311 --> 01:24:25,311
Patience.

1073
01:24:26,021 --> 01:24:27,511
And sacrifice han and Leia?

1074
01:24:27,897 --> 01:24:31,640
If you honor what they fight for... yes.

1075
01:24:31,735 --> 01:24:33,441
If you choose to face vader,

1076
01:24:33,528 --> 01:24:34,813
you will do it alone.

1077
01:24:35,113 --> 01:24:36,774
I cannot interfere.

1078
01:24:38,950 --> 01:24:40,156
I understand.

1079
01:24:45,498 --> 01:24:47,284
R2.

1080
01:24:47,417 --> 01:24:48,827
[Fire up the converters.

1081
01:24:53,840 --> 01:24:56,081
Don't give in to hate.

1082
01:24:56,176 --> 01:24:58,758
That leads to the dark side.

1083
01:24:59,054 --> 01:25:00,339
Strong is vader.

1084
01:25:00,430 --> 01:25:03,342
Mind what you have learned.
Save you it can.

1085
01:25:04,100 --> 01:25:05,100
I will.

1086
01:25:05,435 --> 01:25:06,800
And I'll return.

1087
01:25:06,895 --> 01:25:08,476
I promise.

1088
01:25:16,571 --> 01:25:18,311
Reckless is he.

1089
01:25:18,406 --> 01:25:19,486
Now...

1090
01:25:20,241 --> 01:25:21,651
Matters are worse.

1091
01:25:21,743 --> 01:25:24,029
Obi-Wan: That boy is our last hope.

1092
01:25:24,120 --> 01:25:26,577
No, there is another.

1093
01:25:59,155 --> 01:26:00,216
The ship's almost finished.

1094
01:26:00,240 --> 01:26:02,401
Two or three more things
and we're in great shape.

1095
01:26:02,492 --> 01:26:04,574
The sooner the better.
Something is wrong here.

1096
01:26:04,661 --> 01:26:06,652
No one has seen
or knows anything about 3po.

1097
01:26:06,746 --> 01:26:09,158
He's been gone too long
to have gotten lost,

1098
01:26:09,249 --> 01:26:13,288
relax. I'll talk to lando
and see what I can find out.

1099
01:26:14,045 --> 01:26:16,161
I don't trust lando.

1100
01:26:16,506 --> 01:26:18,588
Well, I don't trust him either.

1101
01:26:18,675 --> 01:26:21,291
But he is my friend. Besides...

1102
01:26:21,386 --> 01:26:23,251
We'll soon be gone.

1103
01:26:24,556 --> 01:26:26,262
Then you're as good as gone,
aren't you?

1104
01:26:59,966 --> 01:27:01,331
Gaahh!

1105
01:27:01,426 --> 01:27:02,461
Leia: What happened?

1106
01:27:04,304 --> 01:27:05,510
Where?

1107
01:27:05,597 --> 01:27:06,882
Gahhh!

1108
01:27:06,973 --> 01:27:08,088
Found him in a junk pile?

1109
01:27:08,641 --> 01:27:11,474
Oh, what a mess.
Chewie, you think you can repair him?

1110
01:27:11,811 --> 01:27:13,722
Gahhh!

1111
01:27:13,813 --> 01:27:15,553
Lando's got people that can fix him.

1112
01:27:15,648 --> 01:27:16,979
No, thanks.

1113
01:27:18,777 --> 01:27:20,768
I'm sorry, am I interrupting anything?

1114
01:27:21,321 --> 01:27:22,606
Not really.

1115
01:27:26,284 --> 01:27:28,366
You look absolutely beautiful.

1116
01:27:28,703 --> 01:27:31,820
You truly belong here with us
among the clouds.

1117
01:27:31,915 --> 01:27:33,405
Thank you.

1118
01:27:33,500 --> 01:27:35,180
Would you join me
for a little refreshment?

1119
01:27:36,336 --> 01:27:37,826
Everyone's invited, of course.

1120
01:27:39,923 --> 01:27:41,413
Having trouble with your droid?

1121
01:27:41,508 --> 01:27:43,169
No, no problem.

1122
01:27:53,102 --> 01:27:54,902
Lando: You see,
since we're a small operation,

1123
01:27:55,271 --> 01:27:58,934
we don't fall into
the jurisdiction of the empire.

1124
01:27:59,025 --> 01:28:00,640
So you're part
of the mining guild, then?

1125
01:28:00,735 --> 01:28:03,943
No, not actually. Our operation
is small enough not to be noticed.

1126
01:28:04,030 --> 01:28:05,941
Which is advantageous for everybody,

1127
01:28:06,032 --> 01:28:10,116
since our customers are anxious to avoid
attracting attention to themselves.

1128
01:28:10,870 --> 01:28:12,781
Aren't you afraid the empire's
going to find out

1129
01:28:12,872 --> 01:28:14,863
about this little operation,
shut you down?

1130
01:28:14,958 --> 01:28:15,958
It's always been a danger

1131
01:28:16,042 --> 01:28:17,770
that looms like a shadow
over everything we've built.

1132
01:28:17,794 --> 01:28:20,285
But things have developed
that'll ensure security.

1133
01:28:20,380 --> 01:28:23,622
I've just made a deal that will keep
the empire out of here forever.

1134
01:28:34,060 --> 01:28:36,927
Darth Vader: We would be honored
if you would join us.

1135
01:28:43,653 --> 01:28:46,315
I had no choice.
They arrived right before you did.

1136
01:28:46,865 --> 01:28:48,071
I'm sorry.

1137
01:28:52,495 --> 01:28:53,985
I'm sorry, too.

1138
01:28:55,915 --> 01:28:57,780
Gahhh.

1139
01:29:08,720 --> 01:29:09,880
No, 3pqo's with them.

1140
01:29:11,431 --> 01:29:13,046
Just hang on. We're almost there.

1141
01:30:10,990 --> 01:30:12,150
Oh, ah, ooh, ah.

1142
01:30:12,617 --> 01:30:14,153
I'm terribly sorry.

1143
01:30:14,243 --> 01:30:16,404
I didn't mean to intrude.
No, please don't get up.

1144
01:30:21,167 --> 01:30:24,000
No! Secret. Stormtroopers?

1145
01:30:24,087 --> 01:30:26,499
Here? We're in danger!

1146
01:30:26,589 --> 01:30:27,999
I must tell the others.

1147
01:30:28,091 --> 01:30:29,171
Oh, no, I've been shot!

1148
01:30:56,703 --> 01:30:58,034
Lord vader.

1149
01:30:58,830 --> 01:31:03,620
You may take captain solo to
jabba the hutt after I have Skywalker.

1150
01:31:03,710 --> 01:31:05,621
Boba: He's no good to me dead.

1151
01:31:05,712 --> 01:31:08,624
Darth Vader: He will not be
permanently damaged.

1152
01:31:10,883 --> 01:31:13,875
Lando: Lord vader,
what about Leia and the wookiee?

1153
01:31:13,970 --> 01:31:16,803
They must never again leave this city.

1154
01:31:16,889 --> 01:31:18,534
That was never a condition
of our agreement,

1155
01:31:18,558 --> 01:31:20,119
nor was giving han
to this bounty hunter.

1156
01:31:20,143 --> 01:31:24,261
Perhaps you think
you're being treated unfairly?

1157
01:31:26,232 --> 01:31:27,267
No.

1158
01:31:27,358 --> 01:31:31,647
Good. It would be unfortunate
if I had to leave a Garrison here.

1159
01:31:33,573 --> 01:31:35,939
This deal is getting worse all the time.

1160
01:31:37,160 --> 01:31:39,572
Oh, yes, that's very good.
I like that.

1161
01:31:39,662 --> 01:31:40,993
Ohl

1162
01:31:41,456 --> 01:31:43,947
something's not right
because now I can't see.

1163
01:31:44,459 --> 01:31:47,826
Oh, oh, oh, that's much better.

1164
01:31:48,671 --> 01:31:50,207
Wait! Wait!

1165
01:31:50,298 --> 01:31:52,630
Oh, my! What have you done?

1166
01:31:52,717 --> 01:31:55,834
I'm backwards,
you flea-bitten furball!

1167
01:31:56,012 --> 01:31:58,924
Only an overgrown mophead like you
would be stupid enough...

1168
01:32:13,571 --> 01:32:14,981
I feel terrible.

1169
01:32:15,073 --> 01:32:16,404
Gahhh.

1170
01:32:30,546 --> 01:32:32,332
Why are they doing this?

1171
01:32:35,259 --> 01:32:37,545
They never even asked me
any questions.

1172
01:32:42,809 --> 01:32:43,969
Lando.

1173
01:32:47,688 --> 01:32:48,808
Han: Get out of here, lando.

1174
01:32:48,856 --> 01:32:50,221
Shut up and listen!

1175
01:32:50,316 --> 01:32:51,877
Vader's agreed
to turn Leia and Chewie over to me.

1176
01:32:51,901 --> 01:32:53,016
Over to you?

1177
01:32:53,111 --> 01:32:54,755
They'll have to stay here,
but at least they'll be safe.

1178
01:32:54,779 --> 01:32:55,779
Leia: What about han?

1179
01:32:55,863 --> 01:32:57,299
Vader's given him to the bounty hunter.
J

1180
01:32:57,323 --> 01:32:58,904
vader wants us all dead.

1181
01:32:58,991 --> 01:33:01,949
He doesn't want you at all.
He's after somebody called Skywalker.

1182
01:33:02,745 --> 01:33:04,952
- Luke.
- Lord vader set a trap for him.

1183
01:33:05,039 --> 01:33:06,119
And we're the bait!

1184
01:33:06,207 --> 01:33:07,947
He's on his way.

1185
01:33:08,876 --> 01:33:11,083
You fixed us all real good, didn't you?

1186
01:33:11,170 --> 01:33:12,876
My friend.

1187
01:33:14,799 --> 01:33:15,879
Stop!

1188
01:33:18,052 --> 01:33:19,462
I've done all I can.

1189
01:33:20,054 --> 01:33:22,716
I'm sorry I couldn't do better,
but I've got my own problems.

1190
01:33:22,807 --> 01:33:24,047
Yeah.

1191
01:33:24,350 --> 01:33:26,261
You're a real hero.

1192
01:33:36,737 --> 01:33:38,693
You certainly have a way with people.

1193
01:33:42,785 --> 01:33:44,446
Ah... ah...

1194
01:33:53,462 --> 01:33:55,623
Darth Vader: This facility is crude,

1195
01:33:55,715 --> 01:33:58,548
but it should be adequate
to freeze Skywalker

1196
01:33:58,634 --> 01:34:01,000
for his journey to the emperor.

1197
01:34:01,095 --> 01:34:03,962
Lord vader,
ship approaching, x-wing class.

1198
01:34:04,056 --> 01:34:07,548
Good. Monitor Skywalker
and allow him to land.

1199
01:34:08,769 --> 01:34:11,932
Lord vader, we only use
this facility for carbon freezing.

1200
01:34:12,023 --> 01:34:13,684
You put him in there, it might kill him.

1201
01:34:13,774 --> 01:34:16,686
I do not want
the emperor's prize damaged.

1202
01:34:16,819 --> 01:34:19,652
We will test it on captain solo.

1203
01:34:43,888 --> 01:34:45,324
C-3poq: If only you'd attached my legs,

1204
01:34:45,348 --> 01:34:47,304
I wouldn't be in
this ridiculous position.

1205
01:34:47,975 --> 01:34:50,887
Now remember, Chewbacca,
you have a responsibility for me,

1206
01:34:50,978 --> 01:34:52,889
so don't do anything foolish.

1207
01:35:06,452 --> 01:35:07,783
What's going on...

1208
01:35:07,870 --> 01:35:09,030
Buddy?

1209
01:35:09,580 --> 01:35:12,037
You're being put into carbon freeze.

1210
01:35:12,124 --> 01:35:15,457
Boba: What if he doesn't survive?
He's worth a lot to me.

1211
01:35:15,544 --> 01:35:18,001
Darth Vader: The empire
will compensate you if he dies.

1212
01:35:18,297 --> 01:35:19,412
Put him in.

1213
01:35:22,176 --> 01:35:23,632
C-3p0o: No, no, no!

1214
01:35:24,262 --> 01:35:26,423
Han: Stop, Chewie, stop, stop!

1215
01:35:27,556 --> 01:35:29,638
C-3pqo: Yes, stop, please!
I'm not ready to die!

1216
01:35:29,725 --> 01:35:32,057
Hey! Hey! Listen to me, Chewie.

1217
01:35:32,478 --> 01:35:33,718
This won't help me.

1218
01:35:33,813 --> 01:35:35,678
Hey, save your strength.

1219
01:35:35,773 --> 01:35:37,309
There will be another time.

1220
01:35:38,609 --> 01:35:40,395
The Princess...

1221
01:35:40,486 --> 01:35:42,317
You have to take care of her.

1222
01:35:44,490 --> 01:35:46,856
Do you hear me? Huh?

1223
01:36:00,381 --> 01:36:01,746
I love you.

1224
01:36:02,174 --> 01:36:03,459
I know.

1225
01:36:24,572 --> 01:36:26,153
Gahhh!

1226
01:36:32,538 --> 01:36:34,574
What's going on? Turn around! J

1227
01:36:34,665 --> 01:36:36,030
Chewbacca, I can't see.

1228
01:36:50,806 --> 01:36:52,717
Gahhh.

1229
01:37:34,517 --> 01:37:37,350
Oh, they've encased him in carbonite.

1230
01:37:37,436 --> 01:37:39,176
He should be quite well-protected,

1231
01:37:39,271 --> 01:37:41,182
if he survived the freezing process,
that is.

1232
01:37:41,273 --> 01:37:43,810
Darth Vader:
Well, calrissian, did he survive?

1233
01:37:43,901 --> 01:37:45,766
Yes, he's alive.

1234
01:37:46,487 --> 01:37:48,318
And in perfect hibernation.

1235
01:37:48,948 --> 01:37:51,360
He's all yours, bounty hunter.

1236
01:37:51,867 --> 01:37:54,074
Reset the chamber for Skywalker.

1237
01:37:56,330 --> 01:37:58,241
Skywalker has just landed, lord.

1238
01:37:58,499 --> 01:38:01,832
Darth Vader: Good. See to it that
he finds his way in here.

1239
01:38:06,465 --> 01:38:11,004
Calrissian, take the Princess
and the wookiee to my ship.

1240
01:38:11,095 --> 01:38:13,281
You said they'd be left in the city
under my supervision.

1241
01:38:13,305 --> 01:38:15,091
I am altering the deal.

1242
01:38:15,182 --> 01:38:17,673
Pray I don't alter it any further.

1243
01:39:54,156 --> 01:39:55,316
Gahhh!

1244
01:39:55,407 --> 01:39:58,069
Luke! Luke, don't, it's a trap!

1245
01:39:59,453 --> 01:40:00,568
It's a a trap!

1246
01:40:46,542 --> 01:40:49,409
Darth Vader:
The force is with you, young Skywalker.

1247
01:40:51,297 --> 01:40:53,754
But you are not a jedi yet.

1248
01:41:55,569 --> 01:41:56,934
Well done.

1249
01:41:58,781 --> 01:42:02,820
Hold them in the security tower.
And keep it quiet. Move.

1250
01:42:08,624 --> 01:42:10,489
What do you think you're doing?

1251
01:42:10,584 --> 01:42:11,624
We're getting out of here.

1252
01:42:11,710 --> 01:42:13,496
I knew all along.
It had to be a mistake.

1253
01:42:13,587 --> 01:42:16,454
Do you think that after what you did
to han, we're going to trust you?

1254
01:42:17,883 --> 01:42:19,168
I had no choice.

1255
01:42:19,259 --> 01:42:20,779
What are you doing?
Trust him! Trust him!

1256
01:42:20,803 --> 01:42:23,795
Oh, we understand, don't we, Chewie?
He had no choice.

1257
01:42:23,889 --> 01:42:25,550
I'm just trying to help.

1258
01:42:25,641 --> 01:42:27,427
We don't need any of your help.

1259
01:42:32,981 --> 01:42:33,981
Leia: What?

1260
01:42:34,066 --> 01:42:35,066
Han...

1261
01:42:35,150 --> 01:42:36,265
It sounds like "han."

1262
01:42:36,360 --> 01:42:38,851
There's still a chance to save han...

1263
01:42:39,738 --> 01:42:42,150
At the east...

1264
01:42:42,241 --> 01:42:43,822
Platform.

1265
01:42:44,368 --> 01:42:45,368
Chewie.

1266
01:42:47,871 --> 01:42:50,283
C-3p0o: I'm terribly sorry
about all this.

1267
01:42:50,374 --> 01:42:52,160
After all, he's only a wookiee.

1268
01:42:52,626 --> 01:42:54,867
Boba: Put captain solo
in the cargo hold.

1269
01:43:10,853 --> 01:43:13,344
C-3p0o: R2, r2, where have you been?

1270
01:43:13,439 --> 01:43:15,270
Wait. Turn around, you woolly...

1271
01:43:16,150 --> 01:43:19,313
Hurry! Hurry! We're trying to save han
from the bounty hunter.

1272
01:43:21,447 --> 01:43:24,314
Well, at least
you're still in one piece.

1273
01:43:24,408 --> 01:43:25,864
Look what's happened to me.

1274
01:43:38,714 --> 01:43:41,000
Oh, no! Chewie, they're behind you!

1275
01:43:54,354 --> 01:43:56,640
You have learned much, young one.

1276
01:43:56,732 --> 01:43:58,814
You'll find I'm full of surprises.

1277
01:44:10,204 --> 01:44:13,571
Your destiny lies with me, Skywalker.

1278
01:44:13,999 --> 01:44:16,285
Obi-Wan knew this to be true.

1279
01:44:16,835 --> 01:44:17,835
No.

1280
01:44:22,382 --> 01:44:23,382
Aaah!

1281
01:44:24,927 --> 01:44:26,463
All too easy.

1282
01:44:31,475 --> 01:44:34,262
Perhaps you're not as strong
as the emperor thought.

1283
01:44:37,314 --> 01:44:38,850
Impressive.

1284
01:44:40,776 --> 01:44:42,357
Most impressive.

1285
01:44:45,030 --> 01:44:46,736
Aaah!

1286
01:44:49,701 --> 01:44:51,657
Obi-Wan has taught you well.

1287
01:44:51,745 --> 01:44:53,781
You have controlled your fear.

1288
01:44:56,250 --> 01:44:57,250
Now...

1289
01:44:57,459 --> 01:44:59,791
Release your anger.

1290
01:44:59,878 --> 01:45:02,585
Only your hatred can destroy me.

1291
01:45:13,642 --> 01:45:14,848
Ohl

1292
01:47:13,220 --> 01:47:15,461
The security code has been changed.

1293
01:47:15,555 --> 01:47:18,797
C-3p0o: R2, you can tell the computer
to override the security systems.

1294
01:47:19,685 --> 01:47:20,800
R I 2, hurry! R2,

1295
01:47:26,108 --> 01:47:28,645
Attention. The empire
has taken control of the city.

1296
01:47:28,735 --> 01:47:32,227
I advise everyone to leave
before more imperial troops arrive.

1297
01:47:38,662 --> 01:47:39,822
This way.

1298
01:47:39,913 --> 01:47:42,450
C-3p0o: Well, don't blame me.
I'm an interpreter.

1299
01:47:42,541 --> 01:47:45,203
I'm not supposed to know a power socket
from a computer terminal.

1300
01:48:06,440 --> 01:48:09,398
Ah! We're not interested in the
hyperdrive on the millennium falcon.

1301
01:48:09,484 --> 01:48:10,484
It's fixed!

1302
01:48:14,364 --> 01:48:16,696
Just open the door, you stupid lump!

1303
01:48:26,209 --> 01:48:27,824
I never doubted you for a second.

1304
01:48:27,919 --> 01:48:28,954
Wonderful!

1305
01:48:53,945 --> 01:48:56,106
Bend down, you thoughtless... ow!

1306
01:49:01,578 --> 01:49:02,613
Leia!

1307
01:49:03,205 --> 01:49:04,240
Gol

1308
01:49:10,712 --> 01:49:13,203
C-3p0o: I thought that hairy beast
would be the end of me.

1309
01:49:14,382 --> 01:49:15,747
Of course I've looked better.

1310
01:50:09,646 --> 01:50:11,011
You are beaten.

1311
01:50:11,523 --> 01:50:13,184
It is useless to resist.

1312
01:50:13,441 --> 01:50:16,524
Don't let yourself be destroyed
as Obi-Wan did.

1313
01:50:27,664 --> 01:50:29,154
Aah!

1314
01:50:32,586 --> 01:50:34,247
There is no escape.

1315
01:50:34,963 --> 01:50:37,249
Don't make me destroy you.

1316
01:50:39,342 --> 01:50:40,377
Luke,

1317
01:50:40,719 --> 01:50:43,927
you do not yet realize your importance.

1318
01:50:44,014 --> 01:50:46,972
You have only begun
to discover your power.

1319
01:50:47,058 --> 01:50:51,347
Join me,
and I will complete your training.

1320
01:50:51,438 --> 01:50:53,804
With our combined strength,

1321
01:50:53,899 --> 01:50:59,360
we can end this destructive conflict
and bring order to the galaxy.

1322
01:50:59,446 --> 01:51:00,982
I'll never join you!

1323
01:51:01,323 --> 01:51:05,236
If you only knew the power
of the dark side.

1324
01:51:06,036 --> 01:51:10,245
Obi-Wan never told you
what happened to your father.

1325
01:51:10,332 --> 01:51:12,118
He told me enough!

1326
01:51:14,794 --> 01:51:16,284
He told me you killed him.

1327
01:51:16,379 --> 01:51:17,744
No.

1328
01:51:17,923 --> 01:51:20,084
I am your father.

1329
01:51:24,471 --> 01:51:25,961
No.

1330
01:51:26,723 --> 01:51:28,088
No.

1331
01:51:28,600 --> 01:51:30,215
That's not true.

1332
01:51:31,686 --> 01:51:33,347
That's impossible!

1333
01:51:33,438 --> 01:51:36,851
Search your feelings.
You know it to be true.

1334
01:51:38,026 --> 01:51:40,517
Nol

1335
01:51:40,820 --> 01:51:43,186
nol

1336
01:51:44,115 --> 01:51:45,195
Luke.

1337
01:51:45,283 --> 01:51:47,524
You can destroy the emperor.

1338
01:51:47,702 --> 01:51:49,658
He has foreseen this.

1339
01:51:49,829 --> 01:51:52,445
It is your destiny.

1340
01:51:52,749 --> 01:51:58,585
Join me, and together we can rule
the galaxy as father and son.

1341
01:52:09,891 --> 01:52:11,256
Come with me.

1342
01:52:11,726 --> 01:52:13,341
It is the only way.

1343
01:52:45,176 --> 01:52:46,256
Ah!

1344
01:53:20,128 --> 01:53:21,368
Ben.

1345
01:53:22,422 --> 01:53:24,128
Ben, please.

1346
01:53:33,808 --> 01:53:35,014
Ben.

1347
01:53:40,273 --> 01:53:41,558
Leia.

1348
01:53:52,160 --> 01:53:53,400
Hear me.

1349
01:53:55,330 --> 01:53:56,615
Leia.

1350
01:53:56,915 --> 01:53:58,325
Luke.

1351
01:54:00,668 --> 01:54:02,329
We've got to go back.

1352
01:54:02,420 --> 01:54:04,376
- What?
- I know where Luke is.

1353
01:54:04,464 --> 01:54:05,579
What about those fighters?

1354
01:54:06,508 --> 01:54:07,918
Chewie, just do it.

1355
01:54:08,009 --> 01:54:09,340
But what about vader?

1356
01:54:09,427 --> 01:54:10,758
All right, all right, all right!

1357
01:54:18,645 --> 01:54:22,684
Darth Vader: Alert my star destroyer
to prepare for my arrival.

1358
01:54:33,410 --> 01:54:35,366
Look, someone's up there.

1359
01:54:36,955 --> 01:54:37,990
Leia: It's Luke.

1360
01:54:38,081 --> 01:54:39,446
Chewie, slow down.

1361
01:54:39,541 --> 01:54:40,951
Slow down. We'll get under him.

1362
01:54:41,042 --> 01:54:42,657
Lando, open the top hatch.

1363
01:54:58,726 --> 01:54:59,966
Leia: Okay.

1364
01:55:00,061 --> 01:55:01,176
Easy, Chewie.

1365
01:55:01,271 --> 01:55:02,306
Gahrrr.

1366
01:55:23,001 --> 01:55:24,001
Lando?

1367
01:55:24,085 --> 01:55:25,165
Okay, let's go.

1368
01:55:42,270 --> 01:55:44,431
Oh, Leia.

1369
01:55:44,731 --> 01:55:46,131
Lando: All right, Chewie, let's go.

1370
01:56:21,643 --> 01:56:22,723
I'll be back.

1371
01:56:29,609 --> 01:56:31,019
Star destroyer.

1372
01:56:36,074 --> 01:56:38,315
Landqo: All right, Chewie.
Ready for light speed.

1373
01:56:38,868 --> 01:56:41,075
Leia: If your people
fixed the hyperdrive.

1374
01:56:41,162 --> 01:56:43,403
All the coordinates are set.
It's now or never.

1375
01:56:43,498 --> 01:56:44,613
Punch it!

1376
01:56:55,635 --> 01:56:57,091
They told me they fixed it.

1377
01:56:57,845 --> 01:56:59,756
I trusted them to fix it!

1378
01:57:00,139 --> 01:57:01,970
It's not my fauit!

1379
01:57:07,855 --> 01:57:10,597
They'll be in range of
our tractor beam in moments, lord.

1380
01:57:10,692 --> 01:57:14,480
Did your men deactivate
the hyperdrive on the millennium falcon?

1381
01:57:14,571 --> 01:57:15,571
Yes, my lord.

1382
01:57:15,655 --> 01:57:20,445
Good. Prepare the boarding party
and set your weapons for "stun."

1383
01:57:20,535 --> 01:57:23,572
- Yes, my lord. Lieutenant.
- Yes, sir.

1384
01:57:24,872 --> 01:57:27,739
Noisy brute.
Why don't we just go into light speed?

1385
01:57:28,167 --> 01:57:29,452
We can't?

1386
01:57:29,752 --> 01:57:32,619
How would you know
the hyperdrive is deactivated?

1387
01:57:35,800 --> 01:57:38,257
The city's central computer told you?

1388
01:57:38,720 --> 01:57:41,632
R2-d2, you know better
than to trust a strange computer.

1389
01:57:41,723 --> 01:57:42,758
Ouch!

1390
01:57:42,849 --> 01:57:44,805
Pay attention to what you're doing!

1391
01:57:55,820 --> 01:57:56,935
Luke.

1392
01:57:57,322 --> 01:57:58,607
Father.

1393
01:58:00,199 --> 01:58:02,531
Son, come with me.

1394
01:58:05,330 --> 01:58:06,740
Ben.

1395
01:58:07,749 --> 01:58:09,740
Why didn't you tell me?

1396
01:58:16,132 --> 01:58:17,132
Chewiel

1397
01:58:28,311 --> 01:58:29,551
It's vader.

1398
01:58:35,360 --> 01:58:38,727
Luke, it is your destiny.

1399
01:58:43,576 --> 01:58:44,782
Ben.

1400
01:58:46,371 --> 01:58:48,202
Why didn't you tell me?

1401
01:58:55,088 --> 01:58:56,919
Alert all commands.

1402
01:58:57,298 --> 01:58:58,879
Ready for the tractor beam.

1403
01:59:01,928 --> 01:59:03,509
R2, come back at once!

1404
01:59:03,596 --> 01:59:05,507
You haven't finished with me yet.

1405
01:59:05,598 --> 01:59:07,384
You don't know
how to fix the hyperdrive.

1406
01:59:07,475 --> 01:59:08,760
Chewbacca can do it.

1407
01:59:08,851 --> 01:59:10,387
I'm standing here in pieces,

1408
01:59:10,478 --> 01:59:12,935
and you're having delusions of grandeur!

1409
01:59:16,818 --> 01:59:18,058
C-3p0o: You did it!

1410
02:00:15,543 --> 02:00:17,625
Luke, we're ready for takeoff.
Y j

1411
02:00:17,712 --> 02:00:18,918
Luke: Good luck, lando.

1412
02:00:20,006 --> 02:00:22,213
When we find jabba the hutt
and that bounty hunter,

1413
02:00:22,300 --> 02:00:23,506
we'll contact you.

1414
02:00:24,010 --> 02:00:26,717
I'll meet you
at the rendezvous point on Tatooine.

1415
02:00:26,804 --> 02:00:28,840
Princess, we'll find han.

1416
02:00:29,098 --> 02:00:30,338
I promise.

1417
02:00:30,433 --> 02:00:32,389
Luke: Chewie,
I'll be waiting for your signal.

1418
02:00:32,685 --> 02:00:34,471
Take care, you two.

1419
02:00:34,562 --> 02:00:36,427
May the force be with you.

1420
02:00:36,522 --> 02:00:37,932
Gahhh.

1421
02:00:38,024 --> 02:00:40,640
Ggahhh.

1422
02:00:49,702 --> 02:00:50,702
Luke: Ow.

